{"tid":1216390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 警察職員facebook有預謀暴打示威者","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:40:54.000Z","uid":71459,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0205619b5e8390a7922306783c24a9c89f2cb668","tid":1216390,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dopw9AG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdopw9AG.png&h=19d50059&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJoh482.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJoh482.png&h=f50f76b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家唔好騷擾人哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2de25ac09fb53618674a7b1883907863e20d27e","tid":1216390,"uid":174207,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"已非專業操守，當年德軍虐打d猶太人都覺得好心涼"},{"pid":"87f51db572f43fda669b00f15df870e4a5dcccb0","tid":1216390,"uid":48379,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"人地返地盤part time又唔得<br />\n唔似有啲人淨係識做狗"},{"pid":"8882242afcba0fcac6d01269a1ea87de0c71a6e2","tid":1216390,"uid":58552,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"好好紀錄呢班反人類罪 殺性上頭嘅黑警<br />\n聯合國受唔受理？"},{"pid":"b24259ef04457320e5e908ece2e885b93677b183","tid":1216390,"uid":226955,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"成班反人類罪嘅蓄生準備上聯合國接受審判啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=f3e8de62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=b17ae7db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=f7bbef25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=8c64b5af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=9ab1074a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=c1d8a15c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議歐美向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0d2ae262cfdb0d0d1c4dfa374d8f68c8d6d8816","tid":1216390,"uid":192024,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"Ho Yuen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />浩園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e447bdc29682c96937ee793f2bb8671e1a8639","tid":1216390,"uid"